dct_title_s: Bird's eye view of holy Jerusalem
dct_alternative_sm: Γενικη Αηοψις Της Αγιας Ηολεως Ιερουσαλημ
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, vegetation, drainage, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of structures, people, camels, and Jesus weeping on a hill above Jerusalem.
Additional text above the neat line in the top margin.
Additional title in Greek at top margin: Γενικη Αηοψις Της Αγιας Ηολεως Ιερουσαλημ.
